features: Provides added warmth and cushioning for Helinox Cots, for use while camping or backpacking in colder weather
Double layer 100g polyester insulation is warm, light, packable, insulation and polyester shell fabric made from 100% recycled materials
Reversible design in prints and colors for style options
Stows in included stuff sack for compact transport
Weighs just 7oz, packs to 13x7x7inches[33x18x18cm], sized to fit a Helinox Cot One
